       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      *=======================
       PROGRAM-ID.      COLPLDCC.
       AUTHOR.          CONSIST.
       DATE-WRITTEN.    30-Apr-93 09:04 PM.

      * Programa Listador de Reporte DCC con Sort.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      *====================
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      *---------------------
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
            DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      *--------------------
       FILE-CONTROL.
      *DOS SELECT GNSSRT         ASSIGN TO SYS001-DA-3330-S-SORTWK1.
      *MVS SELECT GNSSRT         ASSIGN TO        DA-S-SORTWK1.
      *DOS SELECT RPTDCC         ASSIGN TO SYS011-UR-1403-S.
      *MVS SELECT RPTDCC         ASSIGN TO        UT-S-RPTDCC.
           SELECT GNSSRT         ASSIGN TO        DA-S-SORTWK1.
           SELECT RPTDCC         ASSIGN TO        UT-S-RPTDCC.

       DATA DIVISION.
      *=============
       FILE SECTION.
      *------------
       SD  GNSSRT.
       COPY COLRRDCC.
       FD  RPTDCC LABEL RECORDS OMITTED
           REPORT IS RPT-DCC
           .

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *-----------------------
       COPY GNSWGRQA REPLACING ==ADR-REQA== BY ==ADR-DCC-REQA==.
       COPY GNSWGRQA REPLACING ==ADR-REQA== BY ==ADR-TAB-REQA==.
       COPY GNSWGRQA REPLACING ==ADR-REQA== BY ==ADR-MSG-REQA==.
       COPY COLBRDCC.
       COPY GNSWGRQA.
       COPY GNSWGUIB.
       COPY GNSWGELS.
       COPY GNSWVIDD.
       COPY GNSWCFIO.
       COPY GNSWVFIO.
       COPY GNSWGRPT.
       COPY GNSBRTAB.
       COPY GNSBRMSG.
       COPY COLRWDCC.
       COPY GNSWGSYS.
       01  PGM-STAT.
           03 PGM-STAT-SRT            VALUE ' ' PIC X(01).
              88 PGM-STAT-SRT-OKS     VALUE ' '.
              88 PGM-STAT-SRT-MAL     VALUE 'M'.
           03 PGM-SOKS                VALUE ' ' PIC X(01).
           03 PGM-SMAL                VALUE 'M' PIC X(01).
      *<<<< WSS
       COPY GNSBRMSC.
       COPY TABBRUSR.
      *DAD
       COPY GNSWGCPT.
       01  WSS-VARI.
           03  WSS-COD-COCR.
               05  WSS-COD-TOCR                        PIC X(03).
               05  WSS-COD-AOCR                        PIC X(03).
           03  WSS-GLS-DATA.
               05  WSS-GLS-TIO                         PIC X(15).
               05  WSS-GLS-AUX                         PIC X(15).
      *DAD
      *>>>>
      *<<<< WSS_DTC
       COPY GNSWGRQA REPLACING ==ADR-REQA== BY ==ADR-MSC-REQA==.
       COPY GNSWGRQA REPLACING ==ADR-REQA== BY ==ADR-USR-REQA==.
      *>>>>

       REPORT SECTION.
      *--------------
       COPY COLRFDCC.
           .
       COPY COLRTDCC.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      *==================
       DECLARATIVES.
       DEC-PH-DCC SECTION.
           USE BEFORE REPORTING PH-DCC.
       INI-PH-DCC.
       FIN-PH-DCC.
           EXIT.
       END DECLARATIVES.

       MAIN SECTION.
      *------------
       INI-MAIN.
       COPY GNSBGEDB.
           MOVE 'COLPLDCC' TO FIO-PROG.
           PERFORM GNS-BUS-IDD.
           SORT GNSSRT
       COPY COLRSDCC.
           INPUT  PROCEDURE IS INP-SRT
           OUTPUT PROCEDURE IS OUT-SRT.
       FIN-MAIN.
           PERFORM GNS-PRO-END.

       INP-SRT SECTION.
      *---------------
       INI-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-INP TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-DCC.
       FST-INP-SRT.
      *<<<< INI_FST_INP
      *Busca Nombre de la Tabla.
           MOVE 'COL'  TO FIO-SIST.
           MOVE 'DCC'  TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE SPACES TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE FIO-GET-KEY TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM GNS-FIO-TAB.
           IF FIO-STAT-OKS
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB        TO WSS-GLS-DESC
           ELSE
               MOVE 'TABLA SIN REGISTRO PADRE' TO WSS-GLS-DESC.

      *Busca Responsable de la Tabla.
           IF TAB-COD-ATRN IN TAB > SPACES
               MOVE TAB-COD-ATRN IN TAB TO USR-COD-USER IN USR
               PERFORM BUS-USR
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO USR-GLS-DESC.
      *>>>>
           MOVE FIO-GET-FST TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-DCC.
       LUP-INP-SRT.
           IF NOT FIO-STAT-OKS
              GO TO FIN-INP-SRT.
       MOV-INP-SRT.
       COPY COLRMDCC.
           RELEASE SRT.
       NXT-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-GET-NXT TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-DCC.
           GO TO LUP-INP-SRT.
       FIN-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-CLO TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-DCC.

       OUT-SRT SECTION.
      *---------------
       INI-OUT-SRT.
           IF PGM-STAT-SRT-MAL
               GO TO EXT-OUT-SRT.
           OPEN OUTPUT RPTDCC.
           CALL 'GNSPLHDR' USING RPT-VARI.
           INITIATE RPT-DCC.
           RETURN GNSSRT AT END
                GO TO FIN-OUT-SRT.
       LUP-OUT-SRT.
      *<<<< LUP_OUT
      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF DCC-MSC-TCCT IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'               TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'TCCT'              TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE DCC-MSC-TCCT IN SRT TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-DESC IN MSC TO WSS-GLS-TCCT IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-TCCT IN WSS-DCC.

      *BUS-TAB busca glosa de codigo en tabla
           IF DCC-COD-VCAM IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'TAB'               TO TAB-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'VLR'               TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB
               MOVE DCC-COD-VCAM IN SRT TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB
               PERFORM BUS-TAB
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB TO WSS-GLS-VCAM IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-VCAM IN WSS-DCC.

      *DAD
      * Se redefine campo COCR e inicializa glosa de trabajo
           MOVE DCC-COD-COCR IN SRT TO WSS-COD-COCR IN WSS-VARI.
           MOVE SPACES              TO WSS-GLS-DATA IN WSS-VARI.

      * Mediante BUS-TAB busca la glosa del Tipo de Operacion Credito en
      * tabla TIO
           IF WSS-COD-TOCR IN WSS-VARI > SPACES
               MOVE 'TAB'                    TO TAB-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'TIO'                    TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB
               MOVE WSS-COD-TOCR IN WSS-VARI TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB
               PERFORM BUS-TAB
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DCOR IN TAB TO WSS-GLS-TIO IN WSS-VARI.

      * Mediante BUS-TAB busca la glosa de la Clase de Operacion Credito
      * tabla AUX
           IF DCC-COD-COCR IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'               TO TAB-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'AUX'               TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB
               MOVE DCC-COD-COCR IN SRT TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB
               PERFORM BUS-TAB
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DCOR IN TAB TO WSS-GLS-AUX IN WSS-VARI.

      * Se concatenan las glosas de tablas TIO y AUX para desplegarlas j
           MOVE WSS-GLS-DATA IN WSS-VARI TO CPT-STRN.
           PERFORM CPT-BLKS.
           MOVE CPT-STRN TO WSS-GLS-COCR IN WSS-DCC.
      *DAD

      *BUS-TAB busca glosa de codigo en tabla
           IF DCC-COD-PLZO IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'TAB'               TO TAB-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'PZO'               TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB
               MOVE DCC-COD-PLZO IN SRT TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB
               PERFORM BUS-TAB
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB TO WSS-GLS-PLZO IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-PLZO IN WSS-DCC.

      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF DCC-IND-SCRT IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'               TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'SCRT'              TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE DCC-IND-SCRT IN SRT TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-ABRV IN MSC TO WSS-GLS-SCRT IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-SCRT IN WSS-DCC.

      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF DCC-IND-SCTB IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'               TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'SCTB'              TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE DCC-IND-SCTB IN SRT TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-ABRV IN MSC TO WSS-GLS-SCTB IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-SCTB IN WSS-DCC.

      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF DCC-IND-SCBZ IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'               TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'SCBZ'              TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE DCC-IND-SCBZ IN SRT TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-ABRV IN MSC TO WSS-GLS-SCBZ IN WSS-DCC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-SCBZ IN WSS-DCC.

      *BUS-TAB busca datos en tabla PCC.
           IF DCC-GLS-CCSB IN SRT > SPACES
               MOVE 'TAB'               TO FIO-SIST
               MOVE 'PCC'               TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB
               MOVE DCC-GLS-CCSB IN SRT TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB
               MOVE FIO-GET-KEY TO FIO-CMND
               PERFORM GNS-FIO-TAB
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO TAB-CIC-CTAB IN TAB
               MOVE SPACES TO TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB
               MOVE SPACES TO TAB-GLS-ABRV IN TAB.
      *>>>>
       GEN-OUT-SRT.
           GENERATE DL-DCC.
       NXT-OUT-SRT.
           RETURN GNSSRT AT END
                GO TO FIN-OUT-SRT.
           GO TO LUP-OUT-SRT.
       FIN-OUT-SRT.
           TERMINATE RPT-DCC.
           CLOSE RPTDCC.
       EXT-OUT-SRT.
           EXIT.

